title: Well-Seeing Dislike
description: Katie and The Union talk break-up songs they listened to growing up. Travis recaps his date (23:20), Christina had food amnesia (35:23) and Myrtle got to sleep with Katie and Dan last night (41:38). Unfortunately we had another fan acting stupid, this time in Boston (56:44). Naomi Osaka withdraws from the French Open (1:17:25). Do people like Aaron Rodgers on Jeopardy (1:31:52)? We don’t know. What kind of wizard are you (1:49:30)?
